ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 22, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104zcd1665702673944.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zcd1665702673944.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zcd1665702673944.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"zcd1665702673944\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specifies the setting of the ambient UserMode property for all OCXs in a Uniface\n    application.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"zcd1665702673944__topic_d145340e1_d145341e1_d145342e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zcd1665702673944__p_d145343e1_d145344e1_d145345e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">UserMode</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">DESIGN</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">RUN</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zcd1665702673944__section_ep3_nqp_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d807443e68\">Arguments</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"zcd1665702673944__ul_umz_nqp_xvb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zcd1665702673944__li_d50546e1_d50547e1_d50548e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">DESIGN</code>—UserMode for all OCXs is false. The control instance is in a\n          design-time instance of its container, which may have different behavior than the runtime\n          version. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zcd1665702673944__li_d50549e1_d50550e1_d50551e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">RUN</code>—UserMode is true. The control instance is in a running application,\n          so functional behavior is defined by the OCX control. </li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"zcd1665702673944__table_d17708e1_d17709e1_d17710e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">None</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">File section</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"exp1665702673803.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/exp1665702673803.html\" title=\"The [ocx] section of the initialization file is used to specify information about the environment in which OCXs run.\">[ocx]</a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zcd1665702673944__section_o1j_qqp_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d807443e125\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zcd1665702673944__p_d145352e1_d145353e1_d145354e1\">If this setting is not specified, the setting for the\n        ambient UserMode depends on how the application is started:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"zcd1665702673944__ul_unj_rqp_xvb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zcd1665702673944__li_d50552e1_d50553e1_d50554e1\">If the form component is run within the Uniface IDE,\n          UserMode is <code class=\"ph codeph\">false</code>.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zcd1665702673944__li_d50555e1_d50556e1_d50557e1\">In all other cases (including <code class=\"ph codeph\">ide.exe\n            /tst</code>), UserMode is <code class=\"ph codeph\">true</code>. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534385\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534385\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "UserMode Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 22, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specifies the setting of the ambient UserMode property for all OCXs in a Uniface application. UserMode = DESIGN | RUN Arguments DESIGN —UserMode for all OCXs is false. The control instance is in a design-time instance of its container, which may have different behavior than the runtime version. RUN —UserMode is true. The control instance is in a running application, so functional behavior is defined by the OCX control. Default value None File section [ocx] Description If this setting is not specified, the setting for the ambient UserMode depends on how the application is started: If the form component is run within the Uniface IDE, UserMode is false . In all other cases (including ide.exe /tst ), UserMode is true . Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}